# decision-journal-policy
Decision Journal + Outcome Loop — Feb 14, 2026.

Format: @decision id:<slug> date:YYYY-MM-DD domain:<agent-system|projects|marketing|sales|security|personal|other> context:... action:... expected:... metric:... check_on:YYYY-MM-DD status:open next:

Max 120 tokens/decision, 10/week. Status: open|win|loss|mixed|abandoned. Next: keep|tweak|revert|promote-pin|backlog.

STOP-THRASH: Cron fails once → log + ask. Never retry loops.

@decision x-read-only-mode: date:2026-02-14 domain:security context:Rate limits block reactive engagement action:X→read-only, extract ATOMs only expected:Zero rate-limit events metric:blocks/week check_on:2026-02-28 status:open next:keep

