# Habit Layer Governance v1.0 (Airtight Rules)

Implemented comprehensive governance framework for Habit Layer with unambiguous rules.

## Key Features

### Non-Negotiables
- Opt-in crystallization only (no emergent habits)
- Add-Verify-Swap mandatory for all replacements
- Idempotency by default

### Crystallization Triggers (PROPOSE)
| Trigger | Threshold |
|---------|-----------|
| Repetition | >=3/14d OR >=5/30d |
| Tokens | >=1,500 |
| Friction | >=2 failures in 30d |

### Promotion Gates (candidate -> active)  
ALL must pass:
1. Spec completeness (schema, rollback, test_plan)
2. Sandbox test (2x success)
3. Trust pinning (SHA-256)
4. Doctor clean (0 errors)

### Demotion Triggers (active -> disabled)
ANY triggers cooldown:
- consecutiveErrors >=2
- avg outcome_score <=0.40
- Permission violation
- Hash mismatch
-> Cooldown: 24h

### Archive Rules
NEVER auto-archive active. Candidate/disabled only:
- inactive >30d AND uses_30d <1 AND not pinned AND no cron deps

## Implementation

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| habits/GOVERNANCE.md | Full policy |
| habits/QUICKREF.md | Quick reference |
| habits/scripts/propose_habit.js | Trigger validation + proposals |
| habits/scripts/doctor.js | + Governance compliance checks |

## Current State

| Habit | State | Trust | Notes |
|-------|-------|-------|-------|
| rebuild_validate_memory | active | OK | 4 runs, 100% success |
| safe_cron_swap | candidate | OK | Needs 3 successes for promotion |

## Doctor Validation
- Registry schema: OK
- Clear triggers: OK  
- Governance compliance: OK
- Trusted hashes: OK
- Orphaned pins: OK
- Cron deps: OK (8 jobs, 0 habit refs)
- Network deny: OK
- Separation: OK

